  </a>
</p>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal;">
  <a href="https://www.audacy.com/wwjnewsradio/news/national/millions-of-workers-need-to-unretire-to-ease-worker-shortage" target="_blank">Millions of Workers Need to 'Unretire' to Ease Worker Shortage: Study
  </a>
</p>

<h2 style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">
  The Job Market in Boston
</h2>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">Despite concerns over the relentless Delta variant and uncertainty over the new Omicron variant, the U.S. economy continues to create jobs. According to&nbsp;<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/blog/linkedin-workforce-report-december-2021-boston-ma" target="_blank"><b>LinkedIn</b></a>, hiring in Boston was 8.4% higher in November 2021 compared to last month (October 2021), and was 18.8% higher in November 2021 compared to last year (November 2020).
</p>

<br />

<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/blog/linkedin-workforce-report-december-2021-boston-ma" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;" target="_blank">
    <img border="0" data-original-height="1208" data-original-width="1024" height="320" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEglkHDMZaQm6vKnOF1hg_GUlCy_CaQRIpmVR2D7yb9fpRH-g1CjHe6bdDkoWTizQEa7vFV97JR2eNBhyxullgaCETWOMfXCbvpDlWABRuvYJRomgNZQeoDfHiyZ5wInirf_h6f8e21KrhYWNUx35EXB6mItxqBcgJU3h9g9h4pp7ebiCytvCQ=s320" width="271" />
  </a>
</div>

<br />

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">
  The list of <b>Top 20 Web Technologies in Boston</b> has been updated for December. This list is based on keyword searches in job postings at <a href="https://www.indeed.com/lead/indeed-named-top-source-of-hire-north-america" target="_blank"><b>Indeed.com</b></a>. The most in-demand keywords are listed more frequently than less in-demand keywords. This list reflects the change in the last 60 days.
</p>

<h3 style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">
  The Top 20 Web Technologies in Boston
</h3>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">Here are <b>The Top 10</b> of the 20 most in-demand web technologies [<span style="color: green;"><b>UP</b></span> or <span style="color: red;"><b>DOWN</b></span> from mid-October, 2021] ranked by number of job postings on Indeed.
</p>

<h3 style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">
